elebrated.\", \"from\": 583, \"to\": 643, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sakshi Malik, who retired from wrestling last year, and Bajrang Punia were among the first to welcome Vinesh home.\", \"from\": 644, \"to\": 758, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 644, \"end\": 656, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sakshi_Malik\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4077787056152597e-36, \"text\": \"Sakshi Malik\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sakshi_Malik\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sakshi_Malik\"}, {\"begin\": 700, \"end\": 713, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bajrang_Punia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bajrang Punia\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bajrang_Punia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bajrang_Punia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a poignant moment, Vinesh and Sakshi, both of whom have faced immense challenges in their careers, embraced each other and broke down in tears, sharing the weight of their struggles.\", \"from\": 760, \"to\": 945, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 782, \"end\": 788, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vinesh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\"}, {\"begin\": 793, \"end\": 799, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sakshi_Shivanand\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 1.7931477565000778e-13, \"text\": \"Sakshi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sakshi_Shivanand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sakshi_Shivanand\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Later, Sakshi, the 2016 Rio Olympics bronze medallist, wrote on 'X', \\\"Welcome back champion @vineshphogat.\\\"\", \"from\": 947, \"to\": 1054, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 954, \"end\": 960, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sakshi_Shivanand\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 1.7931477565000778e-13, \"text\": \"Sakshi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sakshi_Shivanand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sakshi_Shivanand\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Boxer Vijender Singh, who clinched a bronze medal in 2008 Beijing Olympics, was also at the airport to receive Vinesh.\", \"from\": 1055, \"to\": 1173, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1061, \"end\": 1075, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vijender_Singh\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vijender Singh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vijender_Singh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vijender_Singh\"}, {\"begin\": 1166, \"end\": 1172, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vinesh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Once a champion always a champion #Vineshphogat,\\\" Vijender posted on 'X.'\", \"from\": 1174, \"to\": 1248, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On Friday, Vinesh had expressed her deep sorrow over missing out on the Olympic podium, linking her personal disappointment to the broader struggle for women's rights in India, which she had championed in her protests against the former wrestling federation chief.\", \"from\": 1250, \"to\": 1514, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1261, \"end\": 1267, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vinesh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phoga